Program: Outlook
Title: Arranged Marriages
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsh5
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The husband and wife who spent 13 years living in hiding to avoid an arranged marriage. Lisinka Ulatowska, the woman who went from homelessness to being a globally read author. The story of the adopted woman who unknowingly worked alongside her biological mother. Finally, Bilquis Edhi and the charity in Pakistan collecting unwanted babies. Show less